</a></b></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><cite class=\"citation book\">Altinay, Hakan (2011). <i>Global Civics: Rights and Responsibilities in an Interdependent World</i>. Washington, D.C.: Brookings Institution Press.</cite><span title=\"ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=book&amp;rft.btitle=Global+Civics%3A+Rights+and+Responsibilities+in+an+Interdependent+World&amp;rft.place=Washington%2C+D.C.&amp;rft.pub=Brookings+Institution+Press&amp;rft.date=2011&amp;rft.aulast=Altinay&amp;rft.aufirst=Hakan&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3AGlobal+civics\" class=\"Z3988\"><span style=\"display:none;\">&#160;</span></span></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-4\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><b><a href=\"#cite_ref-4\">^</a></b></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><cite class=\"citation book\">Kagan, Robert (2006). <i>Dangerous Nations</i>. New York: Alfred A. Knopf.</cite><span title=\"ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=book&amp;rft.btitle=Dangerous+Nations&amp;rft.place=New+York&amp;rft.pub=Alfred+A.+Knopf&amp;rft.date=2006&amp;rft.aulast=Kagan&amp;rft.aufirst=Robert&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3AGlobal+civics\" class=\"Z3988\"><span style=\"display:none;\">&#160;</span></span></span>\n</li>\n</ol></div></div>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Further_reading\">Further reading</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/w/index.php?title=Global_civics&amp;action=edit&amp;section=6\" title=\"Edit section: Further reading\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li><cite class=\"citation book\">Altinay, Hakan (2011). <i>Global Civics: Rights and Responsibilities in an Interdependent World</i>. Washington, D.C.: Brookings Institution Press.</cite><span title=\"ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=book&amp;rft.bti